Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.27,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.59,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:01:02.12,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:08.32,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:14.58,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:21.25,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:27.86,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:33.57,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:41.14,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.70,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:49.94,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:56.49,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.43,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:02.79,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:09.72,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 我坚信
